'''梅利莎·泰普'''（{{lang-en|Melissa Tapper}}，{{bd|1990年|3月1日||}}）是一名澳大利亚女子乒乓球运动员。她出生时因为右臂神经损伤，右手不能正常活动<ref name=apc>{{cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org.au/athlete/melissa-tapper/ |title=Melissa Tapper |publisher=Australian Paralympic Committee |location=Australia |year=2012 |accessdate=2012-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229012002/https://www.paralympic.org.au/athlete/melissa-tapper/ |archivedate=2016-02-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。泰普曾在[[2012年夏季残奥会|2012年夏季残奥会]]上获得女子单打10级第四名，之后她参加了2014年英联邦运动会，并携同队友获得了女子团体铜牌<ref>{{cite news|title=Tapper wins spot on able-bodies Glasgow team|url=http://www.standard.net.au/story/2115683/tapper-wins-spot-on-able-bodied-glasgow-team/|newspaper=The Warnambool Standard|accessdate=2016-05-01|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412143011/http://www.standard.net.au/story/2115683/tapper-wins-spot-on-able-bodied-glasgow-team/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月，她在奥运乒乓球大洋洲区外围赛上取得奥运资格，成为史上第一名同时获得奥运会和残奥会两大赛事参赛资格的澳大利亚运动员<ref name="smh">{{cite news|title=Aussie table tennis player Melissa Tapper makes Olympic and Paralympic history|url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics-melissa-tapper-makes-olympic-and-paralympic-history-20160329-gnt95k.html|accessdate=2016-03-30|newspaper=[[雪梨晨鋒報|Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2016-03-29|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815085708/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics-melissa-tapper-makes-olympic-and-paralympic-history-20160329-gnt95k.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rio2016">{{cite web|title=Melissa Tapper|url=http://rio2016.olympics.com.au/athlete/melissa-tapper|website=rio2016.olympics.com.au|publisher=[[澳洲奧林匹克委員會|Australian Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2016-07-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727044227/http://rio2016.olympics.com.au/athlete/melissa-tapper|archivedate=2016-07-27}}</ref>。

==早年经历==
泰普于1990年3月1日出生于维多利亚州汉密尔顿<ref name=apc/>，之后她居住在[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]的郊区<ref name=hamilyon>{{cite news |url=http://www.standard.net.au/story/71135/hamilton-sporting-export-wins-paralympic-selection/ |title=Hamilton sporting export wins Paralympic selection |newspaper=The Warrnambool Standard |date=2012-04-25 |accessdate=2012-07-27 |archive-date=2014-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141201235948/http://www.standard.net.au/story/71135/hamilton-sporting-export-wins-paralympic-selection/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她出生时因为右臂神经损伤，右手不能正常活动<ref name=apc/>。2011年时，她正主攻运动科学的学士学位<ref name=apc/>。2012年时，她已拥有维多利亚体育学院的学位<ref name=visport>{{cite web|url=http://www.vicsport.asn.au/News.aspx?ID=131 |title=Victorian Athletes Selected for London Olympics and Paralympics |publisher=VicSport |accessdate=2012-07-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130410033804/http://vicsport.asn.au/News.aspx?ID=131 |archivedate=2013-04-10}}</ref>。

==运动生涯==
根据乒乓球伤残级别分级，泰普是C10级运动员<ref name=apc/><ref name=abc10>{{cite web |author=Paul Kennedy |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-02-10/contact-sport-friday-10-february/3824058 |title=Contact Sport Friday 10 February |publisher=ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation) |date=2012-02-11 |accessdate=2012-07-27 |archive-date=2012-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120603142226/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-02-10/contact-sport-friday-10-february/3824058 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该级别是除智障级别以外伤残程度最轻的级别<ref name=hamilyon/>。
[[File:Melissa_Tapper_2012.jpg|thumb]]
泰普于2002年开始接触乒乓球，当时她正就读小学<ref name=apc/><ref name=hamilyon/>，她第一次代表澳大利亚国家队出战的赛事是2004年在约旦进行的一场健全人比赛<ref name=apc/>。2004年，她参加了全国乒乓球锦标赛14岁以下级别女子单打、女子双打和混合双打项目，16岁以下级别女子单打、女子双打和混合双打项目以及18岁以下级别女子单打项目的比赛，并获得了其中三个项目的冠军。<ref name=specobserver>{{cite news|url=http://www.spec.com.au/blog/2004/10/07/tappers-talent-again-on-display/ |title=Tapper's talent again on display |newspaper=The Spectator-Observer |date=2004-10-07 |accessdate=2012-07-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121231000808/http://www.spec.com.au/blog/2004/10/07/tappers-talent-again-on-display/ |archivedate=2012-12-31 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>

同年，泰普还在国外参加了两场比赛，分别是捷克的一场比赛以及在葡萄牙举行的世界青少年锦标赛15岁以下级别的比赛<ref name=specobserver/><ref name=spec2>{{cite web|url=http://www.spec.com.au/blog/2004/05/27/tapper-attacks-world-circuit/ |title=Tapper attacks world circuit |publisher=The Spectator-Observer |date=2004-05-27 |accessdate=2012-07-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121231105700/http://www.spec.com.au/blog/2004/05/27/tapper-attacks-world-circuit/ |archivedate=2012-12-31 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>。她所在的学院还为她承担了一部分的出行费用<ref name=specobserver/><ref name=spec2/>。这之后，她开始以参加[[奥运|奥运]]为目标<ref name=hamilyon/>。2008年，她斩获了澳大利亚21岁以下级乒乓球锦标赛以及大洋洲18岁以下级别的冠军<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vis.org.au/athletes/melissa-tapper.html |archiveurl=http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/34944/20110702-0000/www.vis.org.au/athletes/melissa-tapper.html |title=Melissa Tapper |publisher=Victorian Institute of Sport |archivedate=2011-07-02|accessdate=2012-07-27}}</ref>，又获得了迈克尔·绍鲍多什奖澳大利亚年度青少年运动员奖。2008年10月，她参加了在[[印度|印度]][[浦那|浦那]]举行的英联邦青年运动会<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.clearinghouseforsport.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0007/299734/Table_Tennis_Australia_Annual_Report_2008.pdf |publisher=Table Tennis Australia |title=2008 Annual Report |accessdate=2016-05-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330141629/https://www.clearinghouseforsport.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0007/299734/Table_Tennis_Australia_Annual_Report_2008.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-30 }}</ref>。

[[File:040912_-_Melissa_Tapper_-_3b_-_2012_Summer_Paralympics.JPG|thumb]]|left|300x300px]]
2010年，泰普决定出战残疾人乒乓球比赛<ref name=apc/>。2011年时，她的世界排名是第19位<ref name=hamilyon/>。同年3月，她参加了两场分别在意大利和匈牙利举行的比赛，均获得冠军<ref name=apc/>。之后她又在2011年阿拉弗拉运动会上夺得两枚金牌<ref name=stoked>{{cite news|accessdate=2012-07-27|title=Tapper – 'stoked' – by dual – success|newspaper=Sunday Territorian|location=Darwin, Australia|date=2011-05-15|first=Rebekka|last=Wake|page=56|url=http://docs.newsbank.com/openurl?ctx_ver=z39.88-2004&rft_id=info:sid/iw.newsbank.com:AUNB:NTPB&rft_val_format=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:ctx&rft_dat=13743BFA939941F8&svc_dat=InfoWeb:aggregated5&req_dat=1053B823C33F21F9|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304215247/http://docs.newsbank.com/openurl?ctx_ver=z39.88-2004&rft_id=info%3Asid%2Fiw.newsbank.com%3AAUNB%3ANTPB&rft_val_format=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Actx&rft_dat=13743BFA939941F8&svc_dat=InfoWeb%3Aaggregated5&req_dat=1053B823C33F21F9|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外她也成功入选了2012年夏季残奥澳大利亚乒乓球队<ref name=apc/>。在[[2012年夏季残奥会乒乓球比赛|残奥正赛]]上，泰普获得女子单打10级第四名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/olympics/countdown-to-rio-table-tennis-star-melissa-tapper-seeks-a-unique-double-20150910-gjj8t2.html|title=Countdown to Rio: Table tennis star Melissa Tapper seeks a unique double|publisher=[[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2015-09-13|accessdate=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007023926/http://www.smh.com.au/olympics/countdown-to-rio-table-tennis-star-melissa-tapper-seeks-a-unique-double-20150910-gjj8t2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

泰普于2014年入选英联邦运动会澳大利亚代表团。在该届比赛期间她参加女子团体项目和混合双打项目，其中在女子团体项目中，她和队友为澳大利亚队争取到一枚铜牌<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.standard.net.au/story/2445561/hamilton-export-melissa-tapper-wins-bronze-medal-at-commonwealth-games-photos-video/ |accessdate=2016-04-29 |title=Hamilton export Melissa Tapper wins bronze medal at Commonwealth Games |newspaper=The Warrnambool Standard |first=Jarrod |last=Woolley |date=2014-07-29 |archive-date=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602190932/http://www.standard.net.au/story/2445561/hamilton-export-melissa-tapper-wins-bronze-medal-at-commonwealth-games-photos-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是她在主要国际非残疾人赛事上收获的首枚奖牌，而在混合双打项目中，她和搭档[[胡鹤鸣|胡鹤鸣]]在第三轮负于加拿大组合[[张墨|张墨]]和[[王臻|王臻]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.standard.net.au/story/2456585/mixed-doubles-defeat-ends-successful-commonwealth-games-campaign-for-tapper/ |accessdate=2016-04-29 |title=Mixed doubles defeat ends successful Commonwealth Games campaign for Tapper |newspaper=The Warrnambool Standard |first=Jarrod |last=Woolley |date=2014-08-01 |archive-date=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602191530/http://www.standard.net.au/story/2456585/mixed-doubles-defeat-ends-successful-commonwealth-games-campaign-for-tapper/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年9月，她在世界残疾人乒乓球锦标赛上获得女子单打SF10级的铜牌，这是澳大利亚在残疾人乒乓球世锦赛收获的首枚奖牌<ref>{{cite web|title=Tapper wins Australia's first ever ITTF Para-table tennis medal|url=http://www.paralympic.org.au/news/tapper-wins-australia%E2%80%99s-first-ever-ittf-para-table-tennis-medal|publisher=Australian Paralympic Committee |date=2014-09-12|accessdate=2014-09-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310201545/http://paralympic.org.au/news/tapper-wins-australia%E2%80%99s-first-ever-ittf-para-table-tennis-medal |archivedate=2015-03-10}}</ref>。一个月后，她获得了维多利亚体育学院最佳残疾精英运动会奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tabletennis.net.au/news/646-tapper-wins-prestigious-award |title=Tapper wins prestigious award |publisher=HWATT - Health, Wellness & Table Tennis |date=2014-10-28 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531231514/http://tabletennis.net.au/news/646-tapper-wins-prestigious-award |archivedate=2016-05-31 }}</ref>。

2016年3月，泰普参加奥运乒乓球大洋洲区预选赛，并成功进入半决赛，成为史上首位同时获得奥运和残奥资格的澳大利亚运动员<ref name="smh"/>。在里约奥运会上，她参加[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會乒乓球女子單打比賽|女子单打]]和[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會乒乓球女子團體比賽|女子团体]]两个项目，其中在女子单打项目上，她以2比4不敌日裔巴西选手[[卡罗琳·熊原|卡罗琳·熊原]]，止步预赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-08-06/tapper-knocked-out-of-table-tennis-preliminaries/7697662|title=Rio 2016: Melissa Tapper creates history as Australia's first dual Olympian and Paralympian|publisher=ABC News|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708184413/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-08-06/tapper-knocked-out-of-table-tennis-preliminaries/7697662|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在女子团体赛上，澳大利亚最终负于朝鲜，无缘八强<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/table-tennis-standings-tt-womens-team|title=Women's Team|work=Rio 2016|accessdate=2017-06-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922174253/https://www.rio2016.com/en/table-tennis-standings-tt-womens-team|archivedate=2016-09-22}}</ref>。一个月后，她参加[[2016年夏季帕拉林匹克運動會|里约残奥]]，在女子单打10级比赛中，她止步预赛。而在女子团体6至10级项目上，她和搭档Andrea McDonnell获得第四名<ref>{{cite web|title=Melissa Tapper|url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/paralympics/athlete/melissa-tapper-aus|website=Rio 2016|accessdate=2016-11-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203005752/https://www.rio2016.com/en/paralympics/athlete/melissa-tapper-aus|archivedate=2016-12-03}}</ref>。

2018年4月，泰普在黄金海岸举办的英联邦运动会上夺得女子单打TT6至10级的金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/news/gold-coast-2018-melissa-tapper-delights-home-crowd|title=Gold Coast 2018: Melissa Tapper delights home crowd|work=IPC|date=2018-04-14|accessdate=2019-09-21|archive-date=2019-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921110838/https://www.paralympic.org/news/gold-coast-2018-melissa-tapper-delights-home-crowd|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这是她个人在国际主要赛事中获得的首枚残疾人项目金牌。同年10月，她在世界残疾人乒乓球锦标赛上时隔四年再获女子单打SF10级的铜牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://coast.com.au/articles/tapper-wins-bronze/|title=Tapper Wins Bronze|publisher=Coast FM|date=2018-10-22|accessdate=2019-09-21|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190921111412/https://coast.com.au/articles/tapper-wins-bronze/|archivedate=2019-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

